{
  "stem": "18486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not because he was Jewish, but he was not a believer in God.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If he had-- my sister married a Jewish man, and-- but he was a believer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so my parents found that perfectly all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my boyfriend was an atheist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, that was not accepted in my family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- We just-- he was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when-- I was a student-- medical student.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when he made his-- was ready with his-- with his study, he went to Indonesia, on purpose, so that we could-- and I went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we both went to completely different atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he couldn't marry me, because he was an-- an-- an-- how you call that-- he-- he couldn't-- his children couldn't be Jewish when he married to Christian girl.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I lived for a year in Paris, he came and said, you are more dear to me than-- (LAUGHS) than-- than the religion.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so he make up his mind that he want to marry me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "(LAUGHS) I see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was over it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- well, I don't even know who was Jewish and who was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- That was not the point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I liked-- I liked certain festivities and to celebrate with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- the day which is around Easter-- what's that name again?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Passover.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I knew, there was-- there was no anti-Semitism in Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as I know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've never noticed or anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never heard of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Jewish people in Germany would all flee, when Hitler came, to Holland, of course, because they felt safe there.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
